<concept id="_5_1_2_product_concept_and_feature_selection">
    <title>5.1.2 Product Concept and Feature Selection</title>
    <shortdesc>Define what the product should look like and its functions.</shortdesc>
    <conbody>
        <p>Define what the product should look like and its functions. Outline the value it offers.
            To verify this, create an <xref href="8_glossary.dita#mvp">MVP</xref> (Minimum Viable
            Product) to test your concept and list the necessary features to add to the roadmap.
            Features and functions can include:</p>
        <ul id="ul_xjk_wl2_qbc">
            <li>
                <p>Key features</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>Additional features</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>Visual features (interface, branding, integrations)</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </conbody>
</concept>
